        "brief_summary": {
            "textblock": "The DROP study is a prospective, multi center, randomized, open-label trial to test the\n      efficacy and safety of extended catheter pericardial drainage in patients with non-malignant\n      pericardial effusions."
        }, 
        "brief_title": "Drainage or Pericardiocentesis (DROP) Alone for Recurrent Non-malignant Pericardial Effusions Requiring Intervention", 
