        }, 
        "detailed_description": {
            "textblock": "The trial will compared the efficacy and safety of pericardiocentesis alone compared with\n      extended pericardial catheter drainage for the prevention of recurrent effusions in patients\n      with non-malignant pericardial effusions requiring intervention."
        }, 
